This is in unity with the whole life and teaching of Jesus 3 for not only does he not relegate anything except lack of faith to the kingdom of evil, but he so expends energy to express his loathing of the mental attitude of the Pharisees that we cannot suppose he came to save the Church merely into a lai-ger and nobler form of separatism.
